                     <interp inst="t18270913-217-person1914" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am constable of the night; here is the basket and lead. I compared it with what is left in the stable - it matches exactly.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was going to see a young man. I had not touched the basket.</p>
